:: Start [speaker-1]
[timestamp Today 9:41 AM]

hi!

👋

[[hello]]
[[whatsup?!]]


:: hello
this passage without speaker tag is rendered as a meta passage.

[[ok]]

:: ok [speaker-2]
how are you doing?

[[pretty good]]
[[not so well]]


:: whatsup?! [speaker-2]
all good in the hood...

each paragraph of a passage becomes its own message bubble

which makes longer passages feel like a real text exchange 💬

[[where are you from?]]
[[what is your name?]]


:: pretty good [speaker-1]
nice to hear!

what's the weather like where you are? send me a photo ☀️

[[photo:*->photo-reply]]
[[rather not say->Start]]

:: photo-reply [speaker-1]
<% if (s.lastPhoto === 'sunny') { %>gorgeous! enjoy the sunshine 😎<% } else { %>oh no, stay dry out there ☔<% } %>

you've sent me <%= s.sentPhotos.length %> photo(s) so far

[[start over?->Start]]

